    Features:
        - Custom GUI with a draggable radius slider (10-40 studs)
        - Auto Block when ANY player (survivor OR killer) is within your set radius
        - Smart cooldown system to avoid spam-blocking
        - Advanced distance checks optimized for performance
        - Works on JJSploit, Xeno, and most modern executors
    Controls:
        - Toggle the GUI with your hotkey (default: RightShift)
        - Adjust the block radius with the slider
    Coded by: Rebel Dev
